Synopsis: Enables or disables user/computer section of Group Policy.
Description: Enables or disables user/computer section of Group Policy.

Examples.Title: EXAMPLE 1
Examples.Code: Set-GPOZaurrStatus -Name 'TEST | Empty GPO - AD.EVOTEC.PL CrossDomain GPO' -Status AllSettingsEnabled -Verbose

Examples.Title: EXAMPLE 2
Examples.Code: Set-GPOZaurrStatus -Name 'TEST | Empty GPO - AD.EVOTEC.PL CrossDomain GPO' -DomainName ad.evotec.pl -Status AllSettingsEnabled -Verbose
